thread.title: Las Vegas Rally Caps Weekend of Political Activism as Women Focus on 2018 Elections

author: Sara Randazzo
title: Las Vegas Rally Caps Weekend of Political Activism as Women Focus on 2018 Elections
text:
Thousands of people gathered Sunday in Las Vegas for a “power to the polls” rally held on the first anniversary of a wave of marches organized by women across the U.S.
The Las Vegas rally capped a weekend packed with more than 250 events nationwide that aimed to carry on the momentum from last year’s marches held in Washington, D.C., New York, Los Angeles and other major cities.
